Launch
======

16-Dec-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Bugfixes.
Split out the setting of handlers to config.py.

15-Dec-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Better UI: instant action so Apply button gone, feedback on when handler 
set (Thomas Leonard).
Make sure that there is at least a http handler (Thomas Leonard).
When generating commands, ensure that $@ is present (Lennon Cook).

05-Dec-2006 (0.3.0)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Better handling of errors when setting a handler fails.  Don't run the 
migration more than once.

02-Dec-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Almost total rewrite.  Handlers for each scheme defined in 
$XDG_CONFIG_DIR/rox.sourceforge.net/URI.

29-Apr-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added i18n support.

23-Apr-2005 (0.1.4)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use $BROWSER for default http handler.
Require ROX-Lib 2.0.0.

23-Jan-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use varlist option widget from ROX-Lib2.

26-Aug-2004 (0.1.3)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Generic scheme handling via the new varlist option widget.

24-Jun-2004 (0.1.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Updated README.

19-Jun-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added icon.  Added handler for mailto:.

31-May-2004 (0.1.1)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Handle URL's passed via stdin (argument of '-').

26-May-2004 (0.1.0)
~~~~~~~~~~~
First version.  Written in the time it took to listen to the second
disc of Fish Head Curry.

